Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:12.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried coming alone to our usual park.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:16.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a feeling I've never felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:21.66,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a child, frightened by the sound of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.67,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran back along the path home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:33.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky outside the window is too vast. Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:36.13,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, may this reach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:44.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Lord, if you ever grant wishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:50.11,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,grant my wish right now, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:56.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear your voice, I miss you! I want to see you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:01:00.83,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must you already be looking toward tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:06.21,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just brush it off, saying the time has slipped by.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:08.54,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:14.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, and yet it's been too late since long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:19.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I give up, it can't be like the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:24.35,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just decide so simply there's no way, no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:28.23,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.08,0:01:43.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Mom used to tell me all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:46.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Hero of Center City...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:52.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a fire in that coal mine \N13 years ago... A terrible accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:59.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A great number of people working inside \Nbecame trapped with no way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:06.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When the people caught up in the fire \Nstarted giving up and losing the will to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:10.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,a single coal miner stood up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.35,0:02:12.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "Don't give up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:17.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He took the other miners and \Nran into an old passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:25.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But their final hope of escape \Nwas blocked by piles of rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:31.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the flames bearing down on them, \Nthe coal miners didn't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:53.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:07.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That coal miner gave everything \Nhe had to save everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:09.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:12.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:22.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, way to be all gloomy \Nright in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:25.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:31.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't protect him like Dad did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:34.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was a hero like Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:39.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Psy wouldn't have been injured like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:42.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:45.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy ain't no hero in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:48.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad is a hero who protected \Neveryone in Center City!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:51.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That worthless idiot is no hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:52.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:56.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:59.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:22.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even before I met you, I \Nalways admired heroes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.19,0:04:27.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was weak, and a coward...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:32.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Dad was a great man, strong and \Nreliable... Everyone could count on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:34.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be a hero like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:40.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't remember much about Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:45.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A hero... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:57.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Joey? Did \Nyou get picked on again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:04.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You Dad was a hero, and he'd \Nnever cry, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you shouldn't cry so easily, Joey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it, Joey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:24.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll all healed up. They said \NI'll be discharged tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:25.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:26.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:31.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, I got hurt \Nbecause of my own weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:33.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:35.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:38.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:41.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it! That's what's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:43.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why you're my hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:48.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:52.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A hero, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:56.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know a lot about heroes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:57.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:02.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About Heroma-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:09.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brian Jones! He's the hero of Center City!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:10.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brian?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:13.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that name brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:15.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:20.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Ain't no one that doesn't \Nwho worked in the coal mines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm his son, Joseph!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:29.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! You're Brian and Catherine's kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:32.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... My, you've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:38.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy was always thinking about \Nhelping his friends over himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:42.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the reason it happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:45.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He had a habit of tapping his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:49.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm gonna protect them," he'd say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:52.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubting it! He's our hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:06:59.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:03.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad was a hero! For real!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:04.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:13.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:16.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:17.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:18.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:22.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad really was a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:26.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The stories Mom used to tell me were true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:28.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:30.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:32.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to hurry and tell my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:33.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Joey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:46.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis! Hey, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:48.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad really was a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:51.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what everyone said!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:53.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:56.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what other people say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:58.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:00.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you say that about Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:05.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah... You don't remember \Nmuch about him, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:08.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:14.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you say such mean things about Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:17.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you shut up? I've told you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:20.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy ain't no hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:22.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a good-for-nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:26.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:30.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:38.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:40.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:51.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know more about him than anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:34.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:40.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:43.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:49.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to see me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:51.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go away anywhere again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:55.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How are mother and father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:58.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're always worrying about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:09:59.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:05.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And not just our parents... \NEveryone at school, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:07.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't seem that way to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:10.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I met Joey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:11.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:18.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,True... There's no way he could \Ntell you that we clashed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:19.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:22.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't involve yourself with him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:24.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:25.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:28.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:29.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:32.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came today to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:36.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not think we will see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:37.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of our parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:52.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:56.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:58.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Lina?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:01.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:11.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you not to concern \Nyourself with Will any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:13.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:14.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand, Lina?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:16.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:17.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:18.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:21.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:23.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother is not dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:24.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:25.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:45.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Heroman... Why do you think my \Nsister says such mean things about Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:51.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone sings his praises... \NEveryone except her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:55.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is a hero, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:01.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A true hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll try asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:50.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:51.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:54.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time anything happens \Nyou come here to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:56.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about actually moving on, for a change?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:13:00.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you found the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:02.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About what a hero really is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:06.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that... Tell me about Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:11.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that you say Dad isn't a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:16.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he did something \NI just can't forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:19.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:25.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On that day, he left the \Nhouse like he always did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:30.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He promised that he'd be back by 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:35.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the last time I ever saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:13.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After who knows how many days, \NI finally figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was never coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:22.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He forgot the promise he made me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:27.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he may be a hero that saved \Na bunch of people's lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:31.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was thankful to \Nhim, and praised him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But who cares about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:38.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the family he left behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:44.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom was proud of Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:47.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She never said anything \Nbad about him like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:50.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ever see Mom cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:55.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She never showed her tears to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:15:00.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how sad she was...\NNo matter how much in pain she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:02.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She was always smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:05.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:10.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know she must have \Nbeen crying in secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:15.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All alone, so that we wouldn't see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:17.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crying out, "If only he was still here..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:23.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She pushed herself for us... She forced herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And before we knew it, she died...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:30.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:33.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:38.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if everyone around the world looks \Nup to him, and praised what he did...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.32,0:15:41.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:44.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...he'd stayed by our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:53.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He acted all cool and tried too hard \Nto be a hero... That's why he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:56.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's funny, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:16:02.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left for his family \Nis that little dirty helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:10.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd tap his head, and say \N"I'm gonna protect them..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:30.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:34.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:45.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Dad had a \Nhabit of tapping his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He never did anything like that at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.43,0:16:55.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Dad thought about his family \Na lot more than you think, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:03.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm gonna protect them."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:32.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the reason I get up everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:43.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were always with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:57.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad... You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:16.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you tell me where Lina is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:19.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already searched everywhere around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:22.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I can't find her anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:23.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:36.14,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:38.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.96,0:18:46.70,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... No, I'm not really okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:49.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:50.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:52.50,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,What do mean, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:56.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Lina, where are you? Come home imme-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina! Hey, Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my... This is trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:06.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:09.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:38.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:40.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:45.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the sound of waves over \Nthe phone, so I figured...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:50.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have a fight with your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:55.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a fight with my sister about Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:57.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:02.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad died when I was still little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:07.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I don't remember very \Nmuch about him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:10.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:19.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, thanks to that, my sister and I feel \Ncloser to him now than we did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:24.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I didn't mean to bother you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I was trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:30.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:38.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:42.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:47.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to waver anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:50.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:56.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:00.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:16.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet that a new ability \Nhas awakened in Heroman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:22.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about you, Lina?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.25,0:21:25.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you have something you \Nwanted to talk with me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:27.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:33.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't involve yourself with him any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:39.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:41.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:44.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:49.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Denton?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:51.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:54.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:57.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:22:00.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:03.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Denton wanted to \Nknow if you were here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:06.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:32.40,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get to know you better,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.40,0:22:35.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,to go at each other with our true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:41.83,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Your tears and smile are both here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:46.26,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard it is, I won't be scared any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:49.32,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,With both of us, we can go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:54.76,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're the one who taught me that I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:23:02.45,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I mutter the words "I was born to meet you"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.12,0:23:07.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,my unease disappears, and my heart burns stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:14.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. We'll go on together with a sign only we understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:19.30,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Carve out this irreplaceable time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:23.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:28.06,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I live feeling the same heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:30.28,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect you to the very last,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:32.68,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,to protect the promise built up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:40.08,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. We'll go on together with a sign only we understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:45.81,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We are carving out this irreplaceable time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.36,0:23:53.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Heroman:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.35,0:23:55.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't waver any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.21,0:23:57.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to go, and finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.53,0:24:00.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everything is connected."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.15,0:24:02.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Hughes said in a hushed voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.87,0:24:05.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The series of events that seemed \Nisolated at first glance...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.78,0:24:09.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When Joey begins to home in on \Nthe core of all the incidents,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:11.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,communications are cut off \Nfrom the White House...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.42,0:24:16.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Heroman #23: Sortie!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.08,0:24:18.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman... Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.66,0:24:20.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
